## Pre-Trained Model Citations

| Field | Example |
|-------|---------|
| Model name | "Llama 3 70B" |
| Provider | "Meta AI" |
| Version / Date | "2024-04-18" |
| Model card URL | `https://huggingface.co/meta-llama/...` |
| License | "Llama 3 Community License" |
| Fine-tuning details | "LoRA on domain data, 3 epochs" |

